Title: Reminds me of one time when I was giving a tour of the Googleplex to two Korean men as a favor to a ...
Author: Jake Koenig
Summary: Reminds me of one time when I was giving a tour of the Googleplex to two Korean men as a favor to a friend. It was kind of drizzly and they were sharing an umbrella and one of them very earnestly asks me "In American culture would this be considered gay?"
